data.description: Exquisite corner lot gem on a quiet cul-de-sac! This gorgeous 5-bed, 3-bath residence w/a 3-car garage has everything you've ever dreamed of. Make yourself at home in the airy & bright living/dining room showcasing tile flooring in all the right places, picture windows, soaring ceilings, & back patio access. The cozy fireplace in the family room promotes a warm & inviting atmosphere. The kitchen displays staggered cabinetry w/crown moulding, sleek granite counters, recessed & track lighting, SS appliances, & a lovely breakfast bar. Discover the carpeted main retreat boasting vaulted ceilings, an ensuite w/two granite vanities, & mirrored door closets. Wow! Serene backyard includes a covered patio, pavers, & a sparkling pool excellent for year-round entertaining. This value won't last!
